Performance comparison table as grouped bar chart: Configurations on X-axis (FP16 no batch, AWQ INT4 no batch, AWQ INT4 Continuous Batch, AWQ INT4 + Spec Decode). Y-axes: TTFT (ms), TPOT (ms), Throughput (Tok/s). FP16: TTFT 1200, TPOT 65, 15 Tok/s. AWQ: TTFT 700, TPOT 35, 28 Tok/s. AWQ+CB: TTFT 900, TPOT 42, 180 Tok/s. AWQ+Spec: TTFT 850, TPOT 18, 320 Tok/s. Color-coded bars, speedup annotations.